          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The reaction 9Be(g,p)8Li was  measured from threshold",
                " (16.89  MeV)  up  to 57 MeV using the bremsstrahlung",
                " beam   from   Iowa   State    University    electron",
                " synchrotron.  The data were taken in energy steps of",
                " about 0.050 MeV for the first  several  MeV  and  in",
                " energy  steps  of about 1.0 MeV for the remainder of",
                " the yield curve.  A number of small resonances  near",
                " threshold  was  observed.  The giant resonance cross",
                " section reaches a peak value of 2.64 (0.30) mb at an",
                " energy   of   23  MeV,  and  it  processes  a  large",
                " high-energy tail.  The integrated cross  section  to",
                " 56.8 MeV is 41.4 (4.6) MeV*mb."
              ]
            }
          ],
